  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "1.      Strengthening of immunization program through financial and technical support for cold chain, micro plans new vaccine introduction, logistic supply and campaigns.\r\n2.      Financial and technical support to  implement  MNCH and nutrition packages  in new districts ( CB-NCP-3 districts,   RAG in 12 districts, IYCF 15 districts)  \r\n3.      Supportive-supervision, monitoring and evaluation, and generation of disaggregated data (by sex and ethnicity)   supported for quality maintenance of MNCH and nutrition programs with equity].\r\n4.      Technical and financial support to establish new and strengthen old Basic Emergency Obstetric Care, Birthing Centre, Skilled Birth Attendant training sites in UNICEF supported districts.\r\n5.     Logistic and commodity provision supported  for Immunization, IMCI, CB-NCP, FCHV, safe motherhood and nutrition programs"
    },
